  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>296996</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>うーん……今年は
この辺りに目ぼしい獲物が
いないみたいですね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mmm...This year's important prey in this area is nowhere to be seen...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297100</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>やはり、&lt;Red&gt;ユークリッド&lt;White&gt;方面へ
出張った方がいいんでしょうか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>As expected the game is moving to the &lt;Red&gt;Euclid&lt;White&gt; area.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297176</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>ですが、あちらは
強い魔物がいて危険です</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Furthermore, that's the habitat of powerful monsters.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297252</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>何すんのか知らねけど、
オレが手伝うぜ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sorry for butting in but can we help with something?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297296</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>君たち……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You guys...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297352</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>何されてるんですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is something the matter?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297472</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>冬の蓄えをするために
村のみんなで狩りをね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We are deliberating over the village's essential supply.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297472</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>ただ、今年はこの辺りは
獲物が少なくて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But the game in this area is running short...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297552</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>だから、&lt;Red&gt;ユークリッド&lt;White&gt;行く話
してたんだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So that's what you mean by them running off to &lt;Red&gt;Euclid&lt;White&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297592</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>ああ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297636</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Chester&gt;は？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Where's &lt;Chester&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297736</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>それが……わからないんだ。
子どもたちは
留守番してるみたいだけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I have no idea... He's likely taking care of the kids, though.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297880</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>んだよ……
こんな時に……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>At a time like this, really...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297880</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>んじゃあさ、
オレと&lt;Mel&gt;で魔物の方は
なんとかするよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then it's settled. Me and &lt;Mel&gt; will see what we can do about the monsters.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297880</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Red&gt;ユークリッド&lt;White&gt;の方に行こうぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Around &lt;Red&gt;Euclid&lt;White&gt;, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297936</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;、ちょっと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;, hold on...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298004</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>エト、わたしたち、
お手伝いするよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eto, we're just lending a hand.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298052</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;まで……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt;, not you too...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298140</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>困ってる人助けるのが、
『なりきり士』の
仕事なんだから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But of course! It's the job of a Roleplayer to help with trouble!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298192</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>そう、だけド……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, I guess...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298332</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>助かるよ。じゃあ、
僕と&lt;Dio&gt;と&lt;Mel&gt;で、
みんなを護衛していこう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thanks for the help. Then I'll go with you to escort the hunters.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298332</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>みんなは獲物を探すのに
集中してください</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The rest of you should focus on finding our prey.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298388</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>わかりました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Got it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298452</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>うーん……
大丈夫なのかな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I hope everything will be ok...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298528</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>見つけた！　シカだ！
追い詰めるぞ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There it is! It's a deer! Don't let it run away!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298592</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>魔物だ！　魔物がいるぞ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>M-monsters! There are monsters!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298644</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>よし！　出番だぜ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kept us waiting, huh! Finally showing up!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298696</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>に、逃がした！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's running away!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298784</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>よしっ！　よくやった……
って……誰だ？　この矢</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All right! Someone got it! Err...who is this? This arrow...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298836</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>……さぁ……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Huh...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298888</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>…………？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298932</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298988</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>いやぁ、大猟大猟♪</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We did it! That was a huge catch!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299052</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>これでこの冬の蓄えになるな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now we can survive the winter just fine!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>34</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299124</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>おかえり、
ぼくのかわいい双子ちゃん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Welcome back, my lovely twins!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>35</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299172</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>ただいま、エト</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We're back, Eto!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>36</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299236</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>ありがとう、
&lt;Dio&gt;、&lt;Mel&gt;</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thanks a lot, &lt;Dio&gt; and &lt;Mel&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>37</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299284</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>軽いもんだぜ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh c'mon, it was super easy!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>38</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299348</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>おっ、おまえたち
来てたのか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah. You guys came.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>39</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299420</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>あっ！　&lt;Chester&gt;！
どこ行ってたんだよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mister &lt;Chester&gt;! Where you off somewhere?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>40</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299476</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>いや、ちょっと散歩にな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Nah was just goin' for a walk.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>41</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299520</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>42</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299592</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>こんな時に散歩とか
マジ信じられねー</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're not serious you were taking a stroll during this time?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>43</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299660</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>ははっ、手伝いとか
めんどーだしな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hahaha sounded like trouble to help out.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>44</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299720</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>ほんと、&lt;Chester&gt;らしいよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Really, that's so &lt;Chester&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>45</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299796</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>まったく……
&lt;Chester&gt;らしいよ。
ふふっ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hahahaha, yeah you can say that's very like him. Hehehe...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>46</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299872</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>おいっ、見ろよっ！
大量の獲物だぜ！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey look! How can there be more game here!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>47</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299956</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>本当だ！　誰だ！
こんなに獲ってきたの……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There IS more! Who's responsible? We sure need to thank him...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>48</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300012</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>えっ……まさか……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh...So that's how it is...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>49</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300100</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;くんたちのおかげで、
冬の準備もだいぶ整いました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>With the help of &lt;Dio&gt; and &lt;Mel&gt; the winter preparations are complete.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>50</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300180</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>で？　君たちの旅に
僕たちの助けは必要かい？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So, what did you need? You need our help for a new journey?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>51</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300240</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>え？　えっと、それは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>W-well...something like that...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>52</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300300</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>一緒に来てくれんのか！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Y-you can come with us again!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>53</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300388</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>僕たちも手伝ってもらったし、
何かお返しができるならね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thanks to you preparations have been finished earlier than expected. Not only do we have time but this is the least we can do.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>54</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300436</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>も、もちろん！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Th-thanks!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>55</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300528</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>んじゃ、ま、旅の
事情は道々聞くとして、
一緒に行こうかね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I just happened to hear you're travelling, no? Well, count me in.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>56</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300572</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Chester&gt;！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Chester&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>57</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300620</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>何よ、偉そうに</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Watch out guys! He thinks he's a big shot!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>58</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300688</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>な、なんだよ、
おまえいたのかよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>W-what!? Speak for yourself!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>59</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300740</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>いましたよ～だ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Gotcha~!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>60</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300800</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>いるならいるって言えよな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Takes a jerk to know one!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>61</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300896</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>なんで、あんたに
わざわざそんなこと
断らなきゃなんないのよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What, you think just because our o legendary hero &lt;Chester&gt; tells us he'll join our travel we should just let you to!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>62</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300948</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>おまえなぁ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>63</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301044</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>まぁまぁ……&lt;Chester&gt;も
&lt;Arche&gt;も顔を合わせるたび
ケンカするなよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh my... Whenever they meet they gotta argue, don't they?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>64</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301088</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>うふふ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hehehe...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>65</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301144</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>それじゃあ、行こうか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ok, then. Let's go.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>66</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
